David Thomson: I think, Sherry, you might know better, we have a recording of this, and also.

438
01:11:07.830 --> 01:11:17.669
David Thomson: If you're interested, there… you can get that credit for this hour that we spent together, if you're interested in the professional development credits with IBA.

439
01:11:18.020 --> 01:11:25.540
David Thomson: So if you're thinking about a certification or whatever, or if you're keeping up your… your certification, …

440
01:11:25.760 --> 01:11:28.049
David Thomson: Definitely, you should hear back from

441
01:11:28.320 --> 01:11:33.210
David Thomson: The… the… our chapter about… about that via an email.

